'''Pere Laval R.C.A School''' ''(Ecole Père Laval RCA)'' is a primary school in [[Sainte-Croix, Mauritius|Sainte-Croix]], [[Port Louis District]], [[Mauritius]], [[Africa]] operated by the [[Le Diocèse de Port-Louis]], a [[Catholic]] organization.

